com.twiddles.ganesha.functionality
Interface RDFProperty

All Known Implementing Classes:
JenaProperty
public interface RDFProperty

Interface for querying and modifying properties of an RDF resource. A property consists of a property type and a corresponding value. Since this property is describing a resource its type is the predicate and its value is the object of a property statement where the resource is the subject.

See Also:
RDFPredicate, RDFObject
